description:
Reporter: Dan Bowens; Producer: Peter Facini; Photographer: Mauro Brattoli; and Editor: Marilyn Salaway
Jazz master Ron Carter is the most recorded bassist of all-time with well over 2,000 recordings to his credit. Carter recalls joining Miles Davis' second great quintet and what it was like working for and with Davis.
